general.desc: Favelle Favco Bhd manufactures cranes. The product portfolio includes offshore cranes, tower cranes, wharf cranes, rental of cranes, and service and maintenance. The company is also engaged in the design, engineering, and maintenance services for integrated automation solutions, process analyzers, and specialized equipment for various industries.
